  "texts": [
    "The experimental findings demonstrated the strong capacity of the proposed model for performance prediction.",
    "The recall rate was approximately 95%, the precision was approximately 90.7%, the AUC was approximately 82%, and the accuracy rate was approximately 86.6% when the number of neurons was 256.",
    "This model had the best time efficiency of less than 0.3 when compared to the other models.",
    "The RMSE of the ADMF model was 84%, MAE was 66.7%, and MAPE was 21%.",
    "Similarly, the study by Yang and Bai (2022), Jiao (2022) proposed a Factorization Deep Product Neural network model (FDPN) using a sports education dataset available at OULAD for course score prediction."
